metadata.name: Aquatic Reverie
metadata.description:
Aquatic Reverie shows a woman immersed in a mystic underwater world. The woman is portrayed as a dreamer, lost in the reverie of unknown alternate realities. The mood of the artwork is dreamy, mystical, and evocative, inviting the viewer to embark on their own journey of imagination and exploration.
Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT & Exquisite Workers. The largest AI art show, June 2-8, 2023. Curated by Anna Dart & Roger Haus.
